हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: A passionate romance between Liam, the powerful alpha of a werewolf pack, and Rachel, a mysterious hybrid unaware of her true identity. Drawn to each other by an unexplainable pull, they marry in secret, defying his family and igniting Rachel’s deadly jealousy. As sparks fly and secrets unravel, forgotten memories resurface — revealing a forbidden night of love that was stolen from them. Now, desire, danger, and destiny collide in a battle for their love.
